name: THE WRONG WINGS
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Listen to and follow the guide within.

Have you ever been uncomfortable in your own skin doing something that deep down inside if you looked you would know it was not right for you. Our bodies have a way of telling us what’s right and what isn’t and we have an amazing way of overriding our own signals.

Find how you express yourself in the world.

How you live is an expression, what you do and the way you do it is an expression. How you interact with others and nature is expressing who you are. Are you making choices for who you really are or for someone else or what you think you should do? 

There’s a lot of pressure from the outside to conform to what we “should” do. There’s barely time to just sit and find out who we are and what we want. The things that sing from our soul match with people, places and actions on the outside. 

Is your life a mirror of your soul? 
Is it a celebration of your being? 

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
